The Franklin Trust Tower at 166 Montague Street is a landmark in Brooklyn Heights Built in 1892. This Romanesque Revival Masterpiece has been Wonderfully Renovated into a Luxury Loft-Apartment Building of Unparalleled Stature. The Red Limestone Base, Intricate Terra Cotta, Stone Engravings, Tiled Mansard Roof, and Multiple Cornices are Truly a Fiesta for the Eyes. The apartments are of the Highest Standard.
